I love this recipe. I've mixed many PB recipes but I like this one much better over others that I have tried. The only thing I haven't tried yet is the PB Cereal recipe released by Charlie Noble. &#xD;
&#xD;
The only problem is of course the juice starts to taste muddled over time, but that seems to be a problem with TFA Peanut Butter, and not a problem with the recipe itself.
